                  "fill": "$text-primary",
                  "content": "1. 异常分类",
                  "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "hJp2M",
                  "name": "p1",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "所有异常必须按照业务异常(BusinessException)和系统异常(SystemException)进行分类处理。业务异常应包含明确的错误码和用户友好的错误消息。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "0JLbt",
                  "name": "h2",
                  "fill": "$text-primary",
                  "content": "2. 异常处理原则",
                  "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "2MVdM",
                  "name": "p2",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "• 不允许捕获异常后不做任何处理（空catch块）\n• 必须在合适的层级统一处理异常\n• 禁止使用异常控制程序流程\n• 所有未预期异常必须记录完整堆栈信息",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "k00RC",
                  "name": "h3",
                  "fill": "$text-primary",
                  "content": "3. 错误码规范",
                  "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "kOXIn",
                  "name": "p3",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "错误码采用6位数字编码：前2位表示模块，中间2位表示子模块，后2位表示具体错误。例如：100101表示用户模块-认证子模块-密码错误。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
